### Birthday packages — admin CRUD + public browse
###
### Admin routes ({{baseUrl}}/packages/...) require a staff/admin
### access token via {{accessToken}}.
### Public routes ({{baseUrl}}/public/packages/...) require no auth and
### return ACTIVE packages only — what the customer mobile app sees.
###
### Soft-delete behavior: DELETE on an ACTIVE package sets status=INACTIVE
### (it stays visible to admin/staff but disappears from public browse).
### A second DELETE on an already-INACTIVE package hard-deletes it.

### GET /public/packages — list ACTIVE packages (customer-facing)
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/packages

### GET /public/packages/{packageId} — single ACTIVE package
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/packages/REPLACE_ME

### POST /packages — create (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/packages
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Birthday Premium",
  "description": "Cake, decorations, photo session, signature cocktail.",
  "priceUSD": 250,
  "inclusions": [
    "Custom cake (8 inch)",
    "Themed decorations",
    "30-minute photo session",
    "Signature cocktail per guest"
  ],
  "displayOrder": 10,
  "imageUrl": "https://famosofuego.com/assets/packages/birthday-premium.jpg",
  "i18n": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Birthday Premium",
      "description": "Cake, decorations, photo session, signature cocktail.",
      "inclusions": [
        "Custom cake (8 inch)",
        "Themed decorations",
        "30-minute photo session",
        "Signature cocktail per guest"
      ]
    },
    "es": {
      "name": "Cumpleaños Premium",
      "description": "Pastel, decoración, sesión fotográfica, coctel signature.",
      "inclusions": [
        "Pastel personalizado (20 cm)",
        "Decoración temática",
        "Sesión fotográfica de 30 min",
        "Coctel signature por invitado"
      ]
    }
  }
}

### GET /packages — list all (active + inactive) for staff/admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/packages
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### GET /packages/{packageId} — single package
GET {{baseUrl}}/packages/REPLACE_ME
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### PUT /packages/{packageId} — partial update
PUT {{baseUrl}}/packages/REPLACE_ME
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "priceUSD": 275,
  "displayOrder": 5
}

### DELETE /packages/{packageId} — soft-delete (sets status INACTIVE)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/packages/REPLACE_ME
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Customer token rejected by staff-audience authorizer → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/packages
Authorization: Bearer {{customerAccessToken}}
